test_unit_issue_493
  record_type "meta_test"
  suite "issue_493"
  test_file "tests/unit/issue_493.rs"
  pins "The repeated ETH claims are extracted from the OCR text, ETH 2024 $1,700 is contradicted while 2021-2023 stay within_recorded_range, BTC 2024 is contradicted with no ETH-specific path, every supported-language alias parses, and a line naming two assets splits into one claim per asset."
